5860be06a43f73fa72f5234a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/isad2672\" class=\"reviewer-name\">isad2672</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 26, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">J\'utilise Elementor depuis quelques temps et sans ou très peu de connaissances en développement... Il me permet de bâtir des sites jolis et avec un UX Design performant !</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent, just wish it was faster at initial edit load time.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/zhayter88\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/efa379d76326e6aca1f15fba53417d6c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/efa379d76326e6aca1f15fba53417d6c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/zhayter88\" class=\"reviewer-name\">zhayter88</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 23, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Really good.\nI just wish it didn\'t take so long to load each page that I want to edit.\nI wish that when switching pages with Finder, that it didn\'t have to reload the entire Elementor interface and toolkit.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Best of the bunch</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/digizencoza\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/2f053c9cda4988e334949464301360f5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/2f053c9cda4988e334949464301360f5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/digizencoza\" class=\"reviewer-name\">digizencoza</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 23, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">You\'ll search long and hard to find a better builder! Thank you!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">page speed became slower and slower</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/zhiv12\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/cd7cd4468bb385638cb8512961ab9b9d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/cd7cd4468bb385638cb8512961ab9b9d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/zhiv12\" class=\"reviewer-name\">zhiv12</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 22, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Elementor is going downhill. Most changes they are introducing now are quickly reducing the page load speed score - about 20 units had been lost on the mobile speed score during updates introduced in the last two months. \n\nI have looked in the Experimental options and am truly terrified. They are working hard to slow down our websites even more. In a true Orwellian style they are drumming their efforts to optimise Asset loading but forgot to mention that your loading time will increase by about one second or two if you activate their \"improvements\".</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Crashes entire Website</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/womevents\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/8a282e7977c6c15c1ba04c44b5fe13d2?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/8a282e7977c6c15c1ba04c44b5fe13d2?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/womevents\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Daniel Wom <small>(womevents)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 22, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">After deactivating Header and Footer Templates, Elementor is blocking and crashing the original Theme-Header &amp; Footer. Like \"if you dont use me, you will use nothing haha\".\nThats a bullshit page-builder for bullshit retarded wEbDeSiGnErS.\nKeep your hands off of this crap.\nMy Client now pays 3x more money, because of a simple deactivating and repair of elementors crap, now it\'s changed to a complete reinstall and redesign of the whole website.\nMany thanks to elementor crap retard editor.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Best Plugin on the market</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/imranm654\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/aad96f6ab09db413012c9c498f8b2e38?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/aad96f6ab09db413012c9c498f8b2e38?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/imranm654\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Imran <small>(imranm654)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 20, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Best Plugin on the market</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">very good for beginner</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mokarimiyan\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/3dffabfba0b4e2551fb495304fd67993?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/3dffabfba0b4e2551fb495304fd67993?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mokarimiyan\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mokarimiyan</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 19, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">very good for beginner to middle.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">It rocket launched my career</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mathieubinette\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/e4ac4d9e85f6926bbb62c9916b5c68f0?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/e4ac4d9e85f6926bbb62c9916b5c68f0?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mathieubinette\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mathieubinette</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 17, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Before Elementor, I was making my own websites and helped a couple of friends build theirs. But after I began using Elementor, I felt confident enough to offer my services. I can\'t wait to see more features to be added in the next update!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">good</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hesman95\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/c394d2c5a0de54a6ded589914029705d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/c394d2c5a0de54a6ded589914029705d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hesman95\" class=\"reviewer-name\">hesman95</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 17, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">very good</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Spending money on Pro version is not completely worth it</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/djeah\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/2783bf469f0c218adf5dade05828f3a5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/2783bf469f0c218adf5dade05828f3a5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/djeah\" class=\"reviewer-name\">djeah</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 17, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Though I love this website builder, I am giving it 3 stars for the kind of support we receive for Pro version, not worth the money we spend.\n\nRaised multiple tickets in last 2 weeks:\n2 for 3.1 update for custom code\n1 for Mailpoet form integration breaking the editor\n1 for unwanted eicons and fontawesome CSS\n\nNone of them answered! Got replies for three of them all having the same content as if they did not even read the issue! \n\nEarlier I has raised issues where clearly anyone could tell from the website that the fonts in the menu on different pages were different. But the support turned a blind eye to it. Moreover for certain issues (limitations I guess) they ask you to post in the Facebook group as their time is too valuable for them to solve your issue! </div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:145:\"The Elementor Website Builder has it all: drag and drop page builder, pixel perfect design, mobile responsive editing, and more. Get started now!\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:58:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/elementor.3.1.1.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:7:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:62:\"https://ps.w.org/elementor/assets/screenshot-1.gif?rev=1608747\";s:7:\"caption\";s:119:\"<strong>Drag &amp; Drop.</strong> Our instant drag &amp; drop lets you easily place every element anywhere on the page.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:62:\"https://ps.w.org/elementor/assets/screenshot-2.gif?rev=1608747\";s:7:\"caption\";s:137:\"<strong>Visual Resize Control.</strong> Customize the various elements of the page. Resizing images, changing column sizes and much more.\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:62:\"https://ps.w.org/elementor/assets/screenshot-3.gif?rev=1494133\";s:7:\"caption\";s:116:\"<strong>Truly Live Edit.</strong> Changes on the page are displayed in realtime. No need to press update or preview.\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:62:\"https://ps.w.org/elementor/assets/screenshot-4.gif?rev=1608747\";s:7:\"caption\";s:167:\"<strong>Template Library.</strong> Save your pages or sections as templates, so you can easily reuse them again, or choose one of our beautiful pre-designed templates.\";}i:5;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:62:\"https://ps.w.org/elementor/assets/screenshot-5.gif?rev=1608747\";s:7:\"caption\";s:121:\"<strong>Responsive Design.</strong> Create custom settings for desktop, tablet &amp; mobile by switching between devices.\";}i:6;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:62:\"https://ps.w.org/elementor/assets/screenshot-6.gif?rev=1608748\";s:7:\"caption\";s:147:\"<strong>Revision History.</strong> Switch between earlier versions of your page design, so your design process is backed up, every step of the way.\";}i:7;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:62:\"https://ps.w.org/elementor/assets/screenshot-7.gif?rev=1608748\";s:7:\"caption\";s:159:\"<strong>Shape Divider.</strong> Choose from a wide array of shape dividers and separate your sections in endless ways, that until now were simply not possible.\";}}s:8:\"versions\";a:343:{s:5:\"0.1.0\";s:58:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/elementor.0.1.0.zip\";s:5:\"0.1.1\";s:58:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/elementor.0.1.1.zip\";s:5:\"0.1.2\";s:58:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/elementor.0.1.2.zip\";s:5:\"0.1.3\";s:58:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/elementor.0.1.3.zip\";s:5:\"0.1.4\";s:58:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/elementor.0.1.4.zip\";s:5:\"0.1.5\";s:58:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/elementor.0.1.5.zip\";s:5:\"0.1.6\";s:58:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/elementor.0.1.6.zip\";s:5:\"0.1.7\";s:58:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/elementor.0.1.7.zip\";s:6:\"0.10.0\";s:59:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/elementor.0.10.0.zip\";s:6:\"0.10.1\";s:59:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/elementor.0.10.1.zip\";s:6:\"0.10.2\";s:59:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/elementor.0.10.2.zip\";s:6:\"0.10.3\";s:59:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/elementor.0.10.3.zip\";s:6:\"0.10.4\";s:59: