>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alvaroi\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/37e3b86afae8d359ca357c3d2e78cf66?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/37e3b86afae8d359ca357c3d2e78cf66?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alvaroi\" class=\"reviewer-name\">alvaroi</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 16, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">working fine from the first moment\nyou really notice on site speed</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">great plugin!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mdobis\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/3568c212a2cd720b142336cb2f72153b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/3568c212a2cd720b142336cb2f72153b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mdobis\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mdobis</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 11, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">great plugin and very easy to use!</div>\