dpress.org/nixmart\" class=\"reviewer-name\">nixmart</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 19, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">AWESOME WP optimize plugin!\n\nAuthor is very helpful to help me rectifying my problems. And most of it, this plugin do what it says!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very fast and awesome support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/vollcom\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/586a4ee300ca8a61f644a3408a0c83ba?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/586a4ee300ca8a61f644a3408a0c83ba?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/vollcom\" class=\"reviewer-name\">vollcom</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 16, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">very nice Plugin, thx to frank ... but also work on PHP8 ;) </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great plugin and excellent support service</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 sta